overview: There are moments in our lives when all we can think of is hole. If youre a top, you want to eat it, stretch it, stuff it and fuck it. Skin-to-skin. If you're a bottom, you have an itch. And nothing can satisfy you until a fully boned bareback fucker takes your hole. No one understands this better than Ray Diesel, Josh Stone, Atlas Grant, Sherman Maus, Dolf Dietrich, Jake Morgan, Riley Mitchel, and Mateo Fernandez. Their lust will fill and possess you and make you want to Take That Hole 2.
title: Take that Hole 2
